{"id":1777,"date":"2024-09-14T22:16:42","date_gmt":"2024-09-14T22:16:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1777"},"modified":"2024-09-14T22:16:42","modified_gmt":"2024-09-14T22:16:42","slug":"steelixite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/","title":{"rendered":"Steelixite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Steelixite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found on a mountain east of Route 11\u2019s Fallshore Beach. Requires Surf.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Steelix<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Fallshore City<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Fallshore City Pok\u00e9mon Center and go south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-south-from-the-fallshore-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Going south from the Fallshore City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going south from the Fallshore City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the south stairs leading to the Fallshore Beach and start going east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-east-from-the-fallshore-beach.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path east from the Fallshore Beach. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path east from the Fallshore Beach.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue east, even when you exit the city and enter Route 11.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/03-pokemon-unbound-continuing-east-and-going-to-route-11.jpg\" alt=\"Continuing east and going to Route 11. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continuing east and going to Route 11.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually see a set of stairs you can reach after crossing a short body of water using Surf.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/04-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-stairs-at-the-end-of-the-path-east.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the stairs at the end of the path east. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the stairs at the end of the path east.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Steelixite is at the end of the path at the top of the stairs.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/steelixite\/05-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-steelixite.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the Steelixite. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the Steelixite.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1778,"parent":278,"